                                        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Pesquisar e usar hashtags, mencionar outros usuários</p>
                                        <code class="text-xs bg-gray-200 px-2 py-1 rounded mt-1">hashtags</code>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="flex justify-end space-x-3">
                        <button id="cancelConnectBtn" class="inline-flex items-center px-4 py-2 border border-gray-300 shadow-sm text-sm font-medium rounded-md text-gray-700 bg-white hover:bg-gray-50">
                            Cancelar
                        </button>
                        <button id="proceedToAuthBtn" class="inline-flex items-center px-4 py-2 border border-transparent text-sm font-medium rounded-md shadow-sm text-white bg-indigo-600 hover:bg-indigo-700">
                            Continuar
                        </button>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div id="oauthStep2" class="oauth-step">
                    <div class="text-center mb-6">
                        <div class="mb-4">
                            <i class="fas fa-lock text-4xl text-indigo-600"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Autenticação Segura</h4>
                        <p class="text-gray-600">Você será redirecionado para o Instagram para autorizar o acesso.</p>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="bg-blue-50 border border-blue-200 p-4 rounded-lg mb-6">
                        <div class="flex">
                            <div class="flex-shrink-0">
                                <i class="fas fa-info-circle text-blue-400"></i>
                            </div>
                            <div class="ml-3">
                                <h3 class="text-sm font-medium text-blue-800">Importante</h3>
                                <div class="mt-2 text-sm text-blue-700">
                                    <p>Após autorizar, você será redirecionado de volta para o InstaAI Creator. Não feche esta janela durante o processo.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg mb-6">
                        <h5 class="font-medium text-gray-900 mb-2">O que acontecerá:</h5>
                        <ol class="list-decimal list-inside space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-600">
                            <li>Você será redirecionado para instagram.com</li>
                            <li>Faça login com suas credenciais do Instagram</li>
                            <li>Revise as permissões solicitadas</li>
                            <li>Autorize o acesso ao InstaAI Creator</li>
                            <li>Você será automaticamente redirecionado de volta</li>
                        </ol>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="flex justify-end space-x-3">
                        <button id="backToScopesBtn" class="inline-flex items-center px-4 py-2 border border-gray-300 shadow-sm text-sm font-medium rounded-md text-gray-700 bg-white hover:bg-gray-50">
                            Voltar
                        </button>
                        <button id="startAuthBtn" class="inline-flex items-center px-4 py-2 border border-transparent text-sm font-medium rounded-md shadow-sm text-white bg-indigo-600 hover:bg-indigo-700">
                            <i class="fas fa-external-link-alt mr-2"></i> Ir para Instagram
                        </button>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div id="oauthStep3" class="oauth-step">
                    <div class="text-center mb-6">
                        <div class="mb-4">
                            <div class="animate-spin rounded-full h-12 w-12 border-b-2 border-indigo-600 mx-auto"></div>
                        </div>
                        <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Conectando...</h4>
                        <p class="text-gray-600">Aguardando autorização do Instagram</p>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg mb-6">
                        <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-2">
                            <span class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-700">Progresso:</span>
                            <span id="authProgress" class="text-sm text-gray-500">50%</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="w-full bg-gray-200 rounded-full h-2">
                            <div id="authProgressBar" class="bg-indigo-600 h-2 rounded-full" style="width: 50%"></div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="text-center">
                        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-4">Se a janela não abrir automaticamente, clique no botão abaixo:</p>
                        <button id="retryAuthBtn" class="inline-flex items-center px-4 py-2 border border-gray-300 shadow-sm text-sm font-medium rounded-md text-gray-700 bg-white hover:bg-gray-50">
                            <i class="fas fa-redo mr-2"></i> Tentar Novamente
                        </button>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div id="schedulePostModal" class="modal">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-xl max-w-md w-full mx-4">
            <div class="px-6 py-4 border-b border-gray-200">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-900">Agendar Post</h3>
            </div>
            <div class="px-6 py-5">
                <div class="space-y-4">
                    <div>
                        <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-1">Conta Social</label>
                        <select class="shadow-sm focus:ring-indigo-500 focus:border-indigo-500 block w-full sm:text-sm border-gray-300 rounded-md p-2 border">
                            <option>Instagram: @seu_perfil</option>
                            <option>Facebook: Sua Página</option>
                        </select>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div>
                        <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-1">Data e Hora</label>
                        <input type="datetime-local" class="shadow-sm focus:ring-indigo-500 focus:border-indigo-500 block w-full sm:text-sm border-gray-300 rounded-md p-2 border">
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg">
                        <h4 class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-900 mb-2">Resumo do Post</h4>
                        <div class="text-sm text-gray-600 truncate" id="scheduledPostSummary">Seu conteúdo agendado aparecerá aqui...</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="px-6 py-4 border-t border-gray-200 flex justify-between">
                <button id="cancelScheduleBtn" class="inline-flex items-center px-4 py-2 border border-gray-300 shadow-sm text-sm font-medium rounded-md text-gray-700 bg-white hover:bg-gray-50">
                    Cancelar
                </button>
                <div class="space-x-2">
                    <button id="postNowBtn" class="inline-flex items-center px-4 py-2 border border-transparent text-sm font-medium rounded-md shadow-sm text-white bg-green-600 hover:bg-green-700">
                        Publicar Agora
                    </button>
                    <button id="confirmScheduleBtn" class="inline-flex items-center px-4 py-2 border border-transparent text-sm font-medium rounded-md shadow-sm text-white bg-indigo-600 hover:bg-indigo-700">
                        Agendar
                    </button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script>
        document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function() {
            // Global variables
            let avatars = [];
            let generatedImages = [];
            let currentAvatar = null;
            
            // Login/Register functionality
            const loginContainer = document.getElementById('loginContainer');
            const appContainer = document.getElementById('appContainer');
            const loginForm = document.getElementById('loginForm');
            const registerForm = document.getElementById('registerForm');
            const showRegisterBtn = document.getElementById('showRegisterBtn');
            const showLoginBtn = document.getElementById('showLoginBtn');
            const loginBtn = document.getElementById('loginBtn');
            const registerBtn = document.getElementById('registerBtn');
            const logoutBtn = document.getElementById('logoutBtn');

            showRegisterBtn.addEventListener('click', function() {
                loginForm.style.display = 'none';
                registerForm.style.display = 'block';
            });

            showLoginBtn.addEventListener('click', function() {
                registerForm.style.display = 'none';
                loginForm.style.display = 'block';
            });

            loginBtn.addEventListener('click', function() {
                const email = document.getElementById('email-address').value;
                const password = document.getElementById('password').value;
                
                if (email && password) {
                    // Simulate login
                    loginContainer.style.display = 'none';
                    appContainer.style.display = 'block';
                    initializeApp();
                } else {
                    alert('Por favor, preencha todos os campos.');
                }
            });

            registerBtn.addEventListener('click', function() {
                const name = document.getElementById('register-name').value;
                const email = document.getElementById('register-email').value;
                const password = document.getElementById('register-password').value;
                
                if (name && email && password) {
                    // Simulate registration
                    alert('Conta criada com sucesso! Faça login para continuar.');
                    registerForm.style.display = 'none';
                    loginForm.style.display = 'block';
                } else {
                    alert('Por favor, preencha todos os campos.');
                }
            });

            logoutBtn.addEventListener('click', function() {
                appContainer.style.display = 'none';
                loginContainer.style.display = 'flex';
                // Reset forms
                document.getElementById('email-address').value = '';
                document.getElementById('password').value = '';
                document.getElementById('register-name').value = '';
                document.getElementById('register-email').value = '';
                document.getElementById('register-password').value = '';
            });

            // Initialize app
            function initializeApp() {
                loadAvatars();
                updateAvatarSelection();
            }

            // Tab navigation
            const tabLinks = document.querySelectorAll('.tab-link');
            const tabContents = document.querySelectorAll('.tab-content');
            
            tabLinks.forEach(link => {
                link.addEventListener('click', function(e) {
                    e.preventDefault();
                    
                    const tabId = this.getAttribute('data-tab');
                    
                    // Update active tab link
                    tabLinks.forEach(l => {
                        l.classList.remove('border-indigo-500', 'text-gray-900');
                        l.classList.add('border-transparent', 'text-gray-500');
                    });
                    this.classList.remove('border-transparent', 'text-gray-500');
                    this.classList.add('border-indigo-500', 'text-gray-900');
                    
                    // Update active tab content
                    tabContents.forEach(content => {
                        content.classList.remove('active');
                    });
                    document.getElementById(tabId).classList.add('active');
                });
            });
            
            // Dark mode toggle
            const darkModeToggle = document.getElementById('darkModeToggle');
            darkModeToggle.addEventListener('click', function() {
                document.body.classList.toggle('dark-mode');
                
                // Toggle icon
                const icon = this.querySelector('i');
                if (document.body.classList.contains('dark-mode')) {
                    icon.classList.remove('fa-moon');
                    icon.classList.add('fa-sun');
                } else {
                    icon.classList.remove('fa-sun');
                    icon.classList.add('fa-moon');
                }
            });
            
            // AI Model Selection
            const aiModels = document.querySelectorAll('.ai-model');
            aiModels.forEach(model => {
                model.addEventListener('click', function() {
                    aiModels.forEach(m => {
                        m.classList.remove('border-indigo-500', 'bg-indigo-50');
                        m.classList.add('border-gray-300');
                    });
                    this.classList.remove('border-gray-300');
                    this.classList.add('border-indigo-500', 'bg-indigo-50');
                });
            });
            
            // Generate Content Button
            const generateContentBtn = document.getElementById('generateContentBtn');
            const generateContentModal = document.getElementById('generateContentModal');
            const cancelGenerateBtn = document.getElementById('cancelGenerateBtn');
            const progressBar = document.getElementById('progressBar');
            const progressText = document.getElementById('progressText');
            const generatedContent = document.getElementById('generatedContent');
            
            generateContentBtn.addEventListener('click', function() {
                const topic = document.getElementById('contentTopic').value;
                if (!topic) {
                    alert('Por favor, insira um tópico para gerar conteúdo.');
                    return;
                }
                
                generateContentModal.classList.add('active');
                
                // Simulate progress
                let progress = 0;
                const interval = setInterval(() => {
                    progress += 10;
                    progressBar.style.width = progress + '%';
                    
                    if (progress <= 30) {
                        progressText.textContent = 'Analisando tópico...';
                    } else if (progress <= 60) {
                        progressText.textContent = 'Gerando texto com IA...';
                    } else if (progress <= 90) {
                        progressText.textContent = 'Criando imagens...';
                    } else {
                        progressText.textContent = 'Finalizando...';
                    }
                    
                    if (progress >= 100) {
                        clearInterval(interval);
                        setTimeout(() => {
                            generateContentModal.classList.remove('active');
                            progressBar.style.width = '0%';
                            progressText.textContent = 'Iniciando geração...';
                            
                            // Show generated content
                            showGeneratedContent();
                        }, 1000);
                    }
                }, 300);
            });
            
            function showGeneratedContent() {
                // Simulate generated content
                const topic = document.getElementById('contentTopic').value;
                const contentType = document.getElementById('contentType').value;
                const imageCount = parseInt(document.getElementById('imageCount').value);
                
                // Update generated content
                document.getElementById('generatedCaption').textContent = `Ótimo conteúdo sobre ${topic}! Este post foi gerado por IA para engajar seu público.`;
                document.getElementById('generatedHashtags').textContent = `#${topic.replace(/\s+/g, '')} #marketing #socialmedia`;
                document.getElementById('editCaption').value = `Ótimo conteúdo sobre ${topic}! Este post foi gerado por IA para engajar seu público.`;
                document.getElementById('editHashtags').value = `#${topic.replace(/\s+/g, '')} #marketing #socialmedia`;
                
                // Generate and display images
                generateAndDisplayImages(topic, imageCount);
                
                // Show generated content section
                generatedContent.style.display = 'block';
                generatedContent.scrollIntoView({ behavior: 'smooth' });
            }
            
            function generateAndDisplayImages(topic, count) {
                const imagesGrid = document.getElementById('generatedImagesGrid');
                imagesGrid.innerHTML = '';
                
                // Generate image URLs
                generatedImages = [];
                for (let i = 0; i < count; i++) {
                    const imageUrl = `https://picsum.photos/seed/${topic}${i}/300/300.jpg`;
                    generatedImages.push(imageUrl);
                    
                    // Create image element
                    const imageDiv = document.createElement('div');
                    imageDiv.className = 'relative group cursor-pointer';
                    imageDiv.innerHTML = `
                        <img src="${imageUrl}" alt="Generated image ${i + 1}" class="w-full h-40 object-cover rounded-lg">
                        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black bg-opacity-0 group-hover:bg-opacity-30 transition-all duration-200 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
                            <button class="opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 bg-white text-gray-800 px-3 py-1 rounded-md text-sm font-medium">
                                Selecionar
                            </button>
                        </div>
                    `;
                    
                    imagesGrid.appendChild(imageDiv);
                }
                
                // Update main preview with first image
                if (generatedImages.length > 0) {
                    document.getElementById('generatedImage').src = generatedImages[0];
                }
            }
            
            cancelGenerateBtn.addEventListener('click', function() {
                generateContentModal.classList.remove('active');
            });
            
            // Save Changes Button
            const saveChangesBtn = document.getElementById('saveChangesBtn');
            saveChangesBtn.addEventListener('click', function() {
                const caption = document.getElementById('editCaption').value;
                const hashtags = document.getElementById('editHashtags').value;
                
                // Update preview
                document.getElementById('generatedCaption').textContent = caption;
                document.getElementById('generatedHashtags').textContent = hashtags;
                
                alert('Alterações salvas com sucesso!');
            });
            
            // Schedule Post Button
            const schedulePostBtn = document.getElementById('schedulePostBtn');
            const schedulePostModal = document.getElementById('schedulePostModal');
            const cancelScheduleBtn = document.getElementById('cancelScheduleBtn');
            const confirmScheduleBtn = document.getElementById('confirmScheduleBtn');
            const postNowBtn = document.getElementById('postNowBtn');
            
            schedulePostBtn.addEventListener('click', function() {
                const caption = document.getElementById('editCaption').value;
                document.getElementById('scheduledPostSummary').textContent = caption;
                schedulePostModal.classList.add('active');
            });
            
            cancelScheduleBtn.addEventListener('click', function() {
                schedulePostModal.classList.remove('active');
            });
            
            confirmScheduleBtn.addEventListener('click', function() {
                schedulePostModal.classList.remove('active');
                alert('Post agendado com sucesso!');
            });
            
            postNowBtn.addEventListener('click', function() {
                schedulePostModal.classList.remove('active');
                alert('Post publicado com sucesso!');
            });
            
            // Avatar functionality
            const createAvatarBtn = document.getElementById('createAvatarBtn');
            const createAvatarModal = document.getElementById('createAvatarModal');
            const closeAvatarModal = document.getElementById('closeAvatarModal');
            const cancelAvatarBtn = document.getElementById('cancelAvatarBtn');
            const trainAvatarBtn = document.getElementById('trainAvatarBtn');
            const trainAvatarModal = document.getElementById('trainAvatarModal');
            const dropZone = document.getElementById('dropZone');
            const fileInput = document.getElementById('fileInput');
            const uploadedImages = document.getElementById('uploadedImages');
            const avatarName = document.getElementById('avatarName');
            
            createAvatarBtn.addEventListener('click', function() {
                createAvatarModal.classList.add('active');
            });
            
            closeAvatarModal.addEventListener('click', function() {
                createAvatarModal.classList.remove('active');
            });
            
            cancelAvatarBtn.addEventListener('click', function() {
                createAvatarModal.classList.remove('active');
            });
            
            // File upload functionality
            dropZone.addEventListener('click', function() {
                fileInput.click();
            });
            
            dropZone.addEventListener('dragover', function(e) {
                e.preventDefault();
                this.classList.add('dragover');
            });
            
            dropZone.addEventListener('dragleave', function() {
                this.classList.remove('dragover');
            });
            
            dropZone.addEventListener('drop', function(e) {
                e.preventDefault();
                this.classList.remove('dragover');
                
                const files = e.dataTransfer.files;
                handleAvatarFiles(files);
            });
            
            fileInput.addEventListener('change', function() {
                handleAvatarFiles(this.files);
            });
            
            function handleAvatarFiles(files) {
                if (files.length > 0) {
                    uploadedImages.classList.remove('hidden');
                    uploadedImages.innerHTML = '';
                    
                    for (let i = 0; i < Math.min(files.length, 15); i++) {
                        const file = files[i];
                        const reader = new FileReader();
                        
                        reader.onload = function(e) {
                            const img = document.createElement('img');
                            img.src = e.target.result;
                            img.className = 'w-full h-full object-cover rounded';
                            
                            const div = document.createElement('div');
                            div.className = 'aspect-square rounded overflow-hidden border';
                            div.appendChild(img);
                            
                            uploadedImages.appendChild(div);
                        };
                        
                        reader.readAsDataURL(file);
                    }
                }
            }
            
            trainAvatarBtn.addEventListener('click', function() {
                const name = avatarName.value;
                if (!name) {
                    alert('Por favor, dê um nome para o seu avatar.');
                    return;
                }
                
                createAvatarModal.classList.remove('active');
                trainAvatarModal.classList.add('active');
                
                // Start training process
                startAvatarTraining(name);
            });
            
            function startAvatarTraining(name) {
                const trainingSteps = document.querySelectorAll('.training-step');
                const trainingProgress = document.getElementById('trainingProgress');
                const trainingProgressBar = document.getElementById('trainingProgressBar');
                
                let currentStep = 0;
                
                function nextStep() {
                    trainingSteps.forEach(step => step.classList.remove('active'));
                    
                    if (currentStep < trainingSteps.length) {
                        trainingSteps[currentStep].classList.add('active');
                        
                        // Update progress
                        const progress = ((currentStep + 1) / trainingSteps.length) * 100;
                        trainingProgress.textContent = Math.round(progress) + '%';
                        trainingProgressBar.style.width = progress + '%';
                        
                        // Move to next step after delay
                        setTimeout(() => {
                            currentStep++;
                            nextStep();
                        }, 2000);
                    } else {
                        // Training completed
                        setTimeout(() => {
                            trainAvatarModal.classList.remove('active');
                            
                            // Add avatar to list
                            const newAvatar = {
                                id: Date.now(),
                                name: name,
                                style: document.querySelector('#createAvatarModal select').value,
                                image: `https://via.placeholder.com/200?text=${encodeURIComponent(name)}`,
                                createdAt: new Date().toLocaleDateString('pt-BR')
                            };
                            
                            avatars.push(newAvatar);
                            saveAvatars();
                            loadAvatars();
                            
                            alert(`Avatar "${name}" criado com sucesso!`);
                        }, 1000);
                    }
                }
                
                nextStep();
            }
            
            const closeTrainingModal = document.getElementById('closeTrainingModal');
            closeTrainingModal.addEventListener('click', function() {
                trainAvatarModal.classList.remove('active');
                resetTrainingSteps();
            });
            
            function resetTrainingSteps() {
                document.querySelectorAll('.training-step').forEach(step => {
                    step.classList.remove('active');
                });
                document.getElementById('trainingStep1').classList.add('active');
                document.getElementById('trainingProgress').textContent = '25%';
                document.getElementById('trainingProgressBar').style.width = '25%';
            }
            
            // Load and save avatars
            function saveAvatars() {
                localStorage.setItem('instaai_avatars', JSON.stringify(avatars));
            }
            
            function loadAvatars() {
                const saved = localStorage.getItem('instaai_avatars');
                if (saved) {
                    avatars = JSON.parse(saved);
                }
                
                displayAvatars();
                updateAvatarSelection();
            }
            
            function displayAvatars() {
                const avatarsGrid = document.getElementById('avatarsGrid');
                avatarsGrid.innerHTML = '';
                
                if (avatars.length === 0) {
                    avatarsGrid.innerHTML = `
                        <div class="border-2 border-dashed border-gray-300 rounded-lg flex flex-col items-center justify-center h-64">
                            <i class="fas fa-plus-circle text-3xl text-gray-400 mb-2"></i>
                            <div class="text-sm text-gray-500">Criar Novo Avatar</div>
                            <button class="mt-3 inline-flex items-center px-3 py-1.5 border border-transparent text-xs font-medium rounded text-white bg-indigo-600 hover:bg-indigo-700">
                                Começar
                            </button>
                        </div>
                    `;
                    return;
                }
                
                avatars.forEach(avatar => {
                    const avatarDiv = document.createElement('div');
                    avatarDiv.className = 'border border-gray-200 rounded-lg overflow-hidden';
                    avatarDiv.innerHTML = `
                        <div class="h-48 bg-gray-100 flex items-center justify-center">
                            <img src="${avatar.image}" alt="${avatar.name}" class="h-full w-full object-cover">
                        </div>
                        <div class="p-4">
                            <div class="font-medium text-gray-900">${avatar.name}</div>
                            <div class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-1">Criado em ${avatar.createdAt}</div>
                            <div class="mt-3 flex space-x-2">
                                <button class="use-avatar-btn inline-flex items-center px-2.5 py-1.5 border border-gray-300 shadow-sm text-xs font-medium rounded text-gray-700 bg-white hover:bg-gray-50" data-avatar-id="${avatar.id}">
                                    Usar
                                </button>
                                <button class="inline-flex items-center px-2.5 py-1.5 border border-gray-300 shadow-sm text-xs font-medium rounded text-gray-700 bg-white hover:bg-gray-50">
                                    Editar
                                </button>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    `;
                    
                    avatarsGrid.appendChild(avatarDiv);
                });
                
                // Add "Create New Avatar" button
                const createNewDiv = document.createElement('div');
                createNewDiv.className = 'border-2 border-dashed border-gray-300 rounded-lg flex flex-col items-center justify-center h-64';
                createNewDiv.innerHTML = `
                    <i class="fas fa-plus-circle text-3xl text-gray-400 mb-2"></i>
                    <div class="text-sm text-gray-500">Criar Novo Avatar</div>
                    <button class="mt-3 inline-flex items-center px-3 py-1.5 border border-transparent text-xs font-medium rounded text-white bg-indigo-600 hover:bg-indigo-700">
                        Começar
                    </button>
                `;
                createNewDiv.addEventListener('click', function() {
                    createAvatarModal.classList.add('active');
                });
                
                avatarsGrid.appendChild(createNewDiv);
                
                // Re-attach event listeners to use avatar buttons
                document.querySelectorAll('.use-avatar-btn').forEach(btn => {
                    btn.addEventListener('click', function() {
                        const avatarId = parseInt(this.getAttribute('data-avatar-id'));
                        const avatar = avatars.find(a => a.id === avatarId);
                        if (avatar) {
                            currentAvatar = avatar;
                            document.getElementById('use-avatar').checked = true;
                            document.getElementById('avatarOptions').classList.remove('hidden');
                            
                            // Highlight selected avatar
                            document.querySelectorAll('.use-avatar-btn').forEach(b => {
                                b.classList.remove('bg-indigo-600', 'text-white');
                                b.classList.add('bg-white', 'text-gray-700');
                            });
                            this.classList.remove('bg-white', 'text-gray-700');
                            this.classList.add('bg-indigo-600', 'text-white');
                            
                            alert(`Avatar "${avatar.name}" selecionado para uso!`);
                        }
                    });
                });
            }
            
            function updateAvatarSelection() {
                const avatarSelection = document.getElementById('avatarSelection');
                avatarSelection.innerHTML = '';
                
                avatars.forEach(avatar => {
                    const avatarDiv = document.createElement('div');
                    avatarDiv.className = 'border border-gray-300 rounded-md p-2 cursor-pointer hover:border-indigo-500';
                    avatarDiv.innerHTML = `
                        <div class="h-16 w-16 rounded-md overflow-hidden mx-auto">
                            <img src="${avatar.image}" alt="${avatar.name}" class="h-full w-full object-cover">
                        </div>
                        <div class="text-xs text-center mt-1">${avatar.name}</div>
                    `;
                    
                    avatarDiv.addEventListener('click', function() {
                        currentAvatar = avatar;
                        
                        // Highlight selected avatar
                        avatarSelection.querySelectorAll('div').forEach(div => {
                            div.classList.remove('border-indigo-500');
                            div.classList.add('border-gray-300');
                        });
                        this.classList.remove('border-gray-300');
                        this.classList.add('border-indigo-500');
                    });
                    
                    avatarSelection.appendChild(avatarDiv);
                });
            }
            
            // Create Assistant Button
            const createAssistantBtn = document.getElementById('createAssistantBtn');
            const createAssistantModal = document.getElementById('createAssistantModal');
            const closeAssistantModal = document.getElementById('closeAssistantModal');
            const cancelAssistantBtn = document.getElementById('cancelAssistantBtn');
            const saveAssistantBtn = document.getElementById('saveAssistantBtn');
            
            createAssistantBtn.addEventListener('click', function() {
                createAssistantModal.classList.add('active');
            });
            
            closeAssistantModal.addEventListener('click', function() {
                createAssistantModal.classList.remove('active');
            });
            
            cancelAssistantBtn.addEventListener('click', function() {
                createAssistantModal.classList.remove('active');
            });
            
            saveAssistantBtn.addEventListener('click', function() {
                const name = document.getElementById('assistantName').value;
                const tone = document.getElementById('assistantTone').value;
                const prompt = document.getElementById('assistantPrompt').value;
                
                if (name && tone && prompt) {
                    alert(`Assistente "${name}" criado com sucesso!`);
                    createAssistantModal.classList.remove('active');
                    
                    // Reset form
                    document.getElementById('assistantName').value = '';
                    document.getElementById('assistantTone').value = 'professional';
                    document.getElementById('assistantPrompt').value = '';
                    document.getElementById('assistantExample').value = '';
                } else {
                    alert('Por favor, preencha todos os campos obrigatórios.');
                }
            });
            
            // Connect Social Media
            const connectBtns = document.querySelectorAll('.connect-btn');
            const disconnectBtns = document.querySelectorAll('.disconnect-btn');
            const connectSocialModal = document.getElementById('connectSocialModal');
            const closeConnectModal = document.getElementById('closeConnectModal');
            const cancelConnectBtn = document.getElementById('cancelConnectBtn');
            const proceedToAuthBtn = document.getElementById('proceedToAuthBtn');
            const backToScopesBtn = document.getElementById('backToScopesBtn');
            const startAuthBtn = document.getElementById('startAuthBtn');
            const retryAuthBtn = document.getElementById('retryAuthBtn');
            
            let currentPlatform = '';
            
            connectBtns.forEach(btn => {
                btn.addEventListener('click', function() {
                    currentPlatform = this.getAttribute('data-platform');
                    showConnectModal(currentPlatform);
                });
            });
            
            disconnectBtns.forEach(btn => {
                btn.addEventListener('click', function() {
                    const platform = this.getAttribute('data-platform');
                    disconnectAccount(platform);
                });
            });
            
            function showConnectModal(platform) {
                // Update modal content based on platform
                const platformData = {
                    instagram: {
                        name: 'Instagram',
                        icon: 'fab fa-instagram text-pink-600',
                        color: 'pink'
                    },
                    facebook: {
                        name: 'Facebook',
                        icon: 'fab fa-facebook text-blue-600',
                        color: 'blue'
                    },
                    tiktok: {
                        name: 'TikTok',
                        icon: 'fab fa-tiktok text-gray-800',
                        color: 'gray'
                    },
                    linkedin: {
                        name: 'LinkedIn',
                        icon: 'fab fa-linkedin text-blue-700',
                        color: 'blue'
                    },
                    youtube: {
                        name: 'YouTube',
                        icon: 'fab fa-youtube text-red-600',
                        color: 'red'
                    }
                };
                
                const data = platformData[platform];
                if (data) {
                    document.querySelector('#socialIconLarge i').className = data.icon;
                    document.querySelector('#oauthStep1 h4').textContent = `Conectar ao ${data.name}`;
                    connectSocialModal.classList.add('active');
                }
            }
            
            closeConnectModal.addEventListener('click', function() {
                connectSocialModal.classList.remove('active');
                resetOAuthSteps();
            });
            
            cancelConnectBtn.addEventListener('click', function() {
                connectSocialModal.classList.remove('active');
                resetOAuthSteps();
            });
            
            proceedToAuthBtn.addEventListener('click', function() {
                document.getElementById('oauthStep1').classList.remove('active');
                document.getElementById('oauthStep2').classList.add('active');
            });
            
            backToScopesBtn.addEventListener('click', function() {
                document.getElementById('oauthStep2').classList.remove('active');
                document.getElementById('oauthStep1').classList.add('active');
            });
            
            startAuthBtn.addEventListener('click', function() {
                document.getElementById('oauthStep2').classList.remove('active');
                document.getElementById('oauthStep3').classList.add('active');
                
                // Simulate OAuth process
                simulateOAuth();
            });
            
            retryAuthBtn.addEventListener('click', function() {
                simulateOAuth();
            });
            
            function simulateOAuth() {
                let progress = 50;
                const interval = setInterval(() => {
                    progress += 10;
                    document.getElementById('authProgress').textContent = progress + '%';
                    document.getElementById('authProgressBar').style.width = progress + '%';
                    
                    if (progress >= 100) {
                        clearInterval(interval);
                        setTimeout(() => {
                            connectSocialModal.classList.remove('active');
                            connectAccount(currentPlatform);
                            resetOAuthSteps();
                        }, 1000);
                    }
                }, 500);
            }
            
            function resetOAuthSteps() {
                document.querySelectorAll('.oauth-step').forEach(step => {
                    step.classList.remove('active');
                });
                document.getElementById('oauthStep1').classList.add('active');
                document.getElementById('authProgress').textContent = '50%';
                document.getElementById('authProgressBar').style.width = '50%';
            }
            
            function connectAccount(platform) {
                const accountElement = document.querySelector(`[data-platform="${platform}"]`);
                if (accountElement) {
                    // Update UI to show connected state
                    const statusElement = accountElement.querySelector('.inline-flex');
                    const usernameElement = accountElement.querySelector('[data-username]');
                    const buttonElement = accountElement.querySelector('button');
                    
                    statusElement.className = 'inline-flex items-center px-2.5 py-0.5 rounded-full text-xs font-medium bg-green-100 text-green-800';
                    statusElement.textContent = 'Conectado';
                    
                    usernameElement.textContent = platform === 'instagram' ? '@seu_perfil' : 
                                                platform === 'facebook' ? 'Sua Página' :
                                                platform === 'tiktok' ? '@seu_tiktok' :
                                                platform === 'linkedin' ? 'Seu Perfil' :
                                                'Seu Canal';
                    
                    buttonElement.className = 'disconnect-btn inline-flex items-center px-2.5 py-1.5 border border-gray-300 shadow-sm text-xs font-medium rounded text-gray-700 bg-white hover:bg-gray-50';
                    buttonElement.textContent = 'Desconectar';
                    buttonElement.setAttribute('data-platform', platform);
                    
                    // Re-attach event listener
                    buttonElement.addEventListener('click', function() {
                        disconnectAccount(platform);
                    });
                    
                    // Update border style
                    accountElement.className = 'social-account flex items-center justify-between p-4 border border-gray-200 rounded-lg';
                    
                    alert(`${platform.charAt(0).toUpperCase() + platform.slice(1)} conectado com sucesso!`);
                }
            }
            
            function disconnectAccount(platform) {
                const accountElement = document.querySelector(`[data-platform="${platform}"]`);
                if (accountElement) {
                    // Update UI to show disconnected state
                    const statusElement = accountElement.querySelector('.inline-flex');
                    const usernameElement = accountElement.querySelector('[data-username]');
                    const buttonElement = accountElement.querySelector('button');
                    
                    statusElement.className = 'inline-flex items-center px-2.5 py-0.5 rounded-full text-xs font-medium bg-gray-100 text-gray-800';
                    statusElement.textContent = 'Desconectado';
                    
                    usernameElement.textContent = 'Não conectado';
                    
                    buttonElement.className = 'connect-btn inline-flex items-center px-3 py-1.5 border border-transparent text-sm font-medium rounded text-white bg-indigo-600 hover:bg-indigo-700';
                    buttonElement.textContent = 'Conectar';
                    buttonElement.setAttribute('data-platform', platform);
                    
                    // Re-attach event listener
                    buttonElement.addEventListener('click', function() {
                        showConnectModal(platform);
                    });
                    
                    // Update border style
                    accountElement.className = 'social-account flex items-center justify-between p-4 border-2 border-dashed border-gray-300 rounded-lg';
                    
                    alert(`${platform.charAt(0).toUpperCase() + platform.slice(1)} desconectado.`);
                }
            }
            
            // Use Avatar Checkbox
            const useAvatarCheckbox = document.getElementById('use-avatar');
            const avatarOptions = document.getElementById('avatarOptions');
            
            useAvatarCheckbox.addEventListener('change', function() {
                if (this.checked) {
                    avatarOptions.classList.remove('hidden');
                } else {
                    avatarOptions.classList.add('hidden');
                }
            });
            
            // Generate Images Checkbox
            const generateImagesCheckbox = document.getElementById('generate-images');
            const imageOptions = document.getElementById('imageOptions');
            
            generateImagesCheckbox.addEventListener('change', function() {
                if (this.checked) {
                    imageOptions.classList.remove('hidden');
                } else {
                    imageOptions.classList.add('hidden');
                }
            });
            
            // Content Type Change
            const contentTypeSelect = document.getElementById('contentType');
            const imageSizeSelect = document.getElementById('imageSize');
            
            contentTypeSelect.addEventListener('change', function() {
                const contentType = this.value;
                
                // Update image size options based on content type
                imageSizeSelect.innerHTML = '';
                
                if (contentType === 'feed') {
                    imageSizeSelect.innerHTML = `
                        <option value="square">Quadrado (1:1) - Instagram Feed</option>
                        <option value="portrait">Retrato (4:5) - Instagram Feed</option>
                    `;
                } else if (contentType === 'story') {
                    imageSizeSelect.innerHTML = `
                        <option value="story">Story (9:16) - Instagram Story</option>
                    `;
                } else if (contentType === 'reel') {
                    imageSizeSelect.innerHTML = `
                        <option value="reel">Reel (9:16) - Instagram Reel</option>
                    `;
                } else if (contentType === 'carousel') {
                    imageSizeSelect.innerHTML = `
                        <option value="square">Quadrado (1:1) - Instagram Carousel</option>
                    `;
                    // Update image count options for carousel
                    const imageCountSelect = document.getElementById('imageCount');
                    imageCountSelect.innerHTML = `
                        <option value="2">2</option>
                        <option value="3">3</option>
                        <option value="4">4</option>
                        <option value="5">5</option>
                        <option value="6">6</option>
                        <option value="7">7</option>
                        <option value="8">8</option>
                        <option value="9">9</option>
                        <option value="10">10</option>
                    `;
                }
            });
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html>
